name: Sims4cheatertool
tagline: Just a small cheater Tool for The Sims 4
body:
### Welcome to the Sims 4 cheater Tool!.
This tool is written in AutoHotKey and it's master use is to help people in The Sims 4.
It can give you more money, level up your Sims and much more.
Feel free to fork this Repository and make your own tool, but don't forget to mention me and add a link to my github page.

### Support
Having trouble with this tool or have questions? Feel free to [contact me](https://undercover-studios.de) on my website.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
